"{\"uid\": \"dailyadvertiser.com.au-story-8669792-illabo-level-crossing-on-olympic-highway-an-overall-positive\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Your digital subscription includes access to content from all our websites in your region.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 90, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Access unlimited content and the digital versions of our print editions - Today's Paper.\", \"from\": 92, \"to\": 180, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Norman family has resided on their family farm at Illabo for more than 100 years and are welcoming news the village's notorious level crossing will be removed.\", \"from\": 182, \"to\": 345, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 186, \"end\": 192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\", \"score\": 0.5467592563588555, \"rank\": 0.4583510889281327, \"text\": \"Norman\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\"}, {\"begin\": 236, \"end\": 242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Illabo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Illabo\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Illabo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Illabo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Loginor signup to continue reading  TheHarris Gates railway crossing on the Olympic Highway, about three kilometres east of Illabo, will be removed and an overpass put in, sharing in a $70 allocation in the 2024-25 state budget.\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 471, \"end\": 477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Illabo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Illabo\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Illabo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Illabo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray Norman's farm is not going to be affected by the project, which changes his perspective on the matter as he understands the impacts it will have on some other landowners.\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 577, \"end\": 583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murray_River\", \"score\": 0.9999999999445208, \"rank\": 5.561919717825965e-11, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murray_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Murray_River\"}, {\"begin\": 584, \"end\": 590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\", \"score\": 0.5467592563588555, \"rank\": 0.4583510889281327, \"text\": \"Norman\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are on the side unaffected by it but the farms on the other side are being greatly affected,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 862, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If you are in the farms where it's going through, it's hideous.\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a complicated issue.\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The farms it goes through and the areas the crossing goes through need to be cared for and need to be thought through.\\\"\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 1076, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That being said, money being put into smaller communities is important.\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1149, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Money needs to be put in so those communities do not get short changed,\\\" Mr Norman said.\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1240, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1228, \"end\": 1234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\", \"score\": 0.5467592563588555, \"rank\": 0.4583510889281327, \"text\": \"Norman\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's cutting farms up which is not great but it does also provide the means of providing a railway between Melbourne and Brisbane.\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1373, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1350, \"end\": 1359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Cross_railway_station\", \"score\": 0.789342185541195, \"rank\": 0.26686523443487187, \"text\": \"Melbourne\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Cross_railway_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_Cross_railway_station\"}, {\"begin\": 1364, \"end\": 1372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"score\": 0.9999406725815565, \"rank\": 5.889278837911148e-05, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Definitely we would see it as a positive, it's a great infrastructure project.\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1454, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If our farm was on the other side then that would not be good.\\\"\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1520, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Norman said it is no secret level crossings are notoriously dangerous and the site of many crashes.\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1525, \"end\": 1531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\", \"score\": 0.5467592563588555, \"rank\": 0.4583510889281327, \"text\": \"Norman\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Harris Gates level crossing is no different.\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1674, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Level crossings are dangerous.\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1707, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There have been accidents on level crossings,\\\" Mr Norman said.\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1758, \"end\": 1764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\", \"score\": 0.5467592563588555, \"rank\": 0.4583510889281327, \"text\": \"Norman\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Normans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As they are building the railway it is good for the crossings to be fixed, to be worked through, the government does also need to work towards a budget across the whole line as well.\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1955, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If we are going to produce food for the world, if we are going to have industry inland, if we can not transport it you can not have industry, you can not have production and the government making these bold steps is really important for local communities.\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 2213, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If we want jobs, if we want prosperity in the regions, in the bush, we have to expect that when the government puts up opportunities like this we have to support it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2382, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His son Tom Norman is of a similar mind, welcoming the project.\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2392, \"end\": 2402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Norman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Norman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Norman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Norman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The new change will be good, it will definitely come with some difficulties but I think overall it will definitely come as a benefit,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2593, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Australian and NSW governments have committed to a program of work to improve the safety and reliability at road and rail interfaces on the Inland Rail route.\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2757, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2595, \"end\": 2609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.107798158937858e-29, \"text\": \"The Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\"}, {\"begin\": 2614, \"end\": 2617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_South_Wales\", \"score\": 0.9952485850093115, \"rank\": 0.0047740967170438785, \"text\": \"NSW\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_South_Wales\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_South_Wales\"}, {\"begin\": 2739, \"end\": 2750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Inland_Rail\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Inland Rail\", \"types\": [\"Q728937\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Inland_Rail\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Inland_Rail\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The appointed $70 million will be distributed between the Harris Gates crossing and the Newell Highway crossing at Tichborne, south of Parkes.\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2901, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2874, \"end\": 2883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_Frontenac\", \"score\": 0.9763221058127476, \"rank\": 0.024252133641633575, \"text\": \"Tichborne\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_Frontenac\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_Frontenac\"}, {\"begin\": 2894, \"end\": 2900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Parkes\", \"score\": 0.9998193485125012, \"rank\": 0.00015939306335623825, \"text\": \"Parkes\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Parkes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Henry_Parkes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A spokesperson for Transport for NSW said the projects are currently under development and the next steps will be communicated to the community and key stakeholders once a project timeline is finalised.\", \"from\": 2903, \"to\": 31